{
  "stem": "1873.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "But he didn't give the gun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And they left, promising that they'd find out, buy food, and come back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "They did never come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And finally, it starts to be daytime, daylight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And we realized, we are out from the forest, left alone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And a  terrible thing happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "At that point, terrible things happened, because the healthy people, young people, did get together and tried to sneak away from the women, from the old people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And we, in turn, didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And we did try to go with the young people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "There were fights.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally, we were-- I did go immediately to my friend, Weizen, which was a friend in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told  him, listen, there's no way we could survive now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't have weapons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you want to go with me?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, did they-- do you think that they had to continue their loyalty to each other?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, from the distance of the history, I know that, only, that not far from our place in the Parczew forest, so-called 'Parchev' forest, there were-- there was-- not far from Sobibor-- there was a group, Chil Grynszpan's group.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were Jewish partisan groups with family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I imagine that he, with his experience in having-- we had rifles and guns, 10 of them, 11.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He could form a fighting unit, a very good fighting units, because we weren't simple people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- we have seen our end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We  weren't dreaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have seen it with our eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would fight till the last gasp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He could go with us to the forest, be a leader.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But he didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I met him in Russia, we talked about this, because, you see, I don't blame him.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
